{"tid":931985,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普准用致命武器對付人蛇","createTime":"2018-12-07T11:45:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-07T16:17:52.000Z","uid":149978,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b877adc8a24aa69c17c78b5689fe87375d53c9b2","tid":931985,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T11:45:09.000Z","msg":"特朗普准用致命武器對付人蛇<br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】（星島日報報道）美國總統特朗普周四在感恩節威脅說，南部邊境駐軍已授權使用「致命武器」，阻止中美洲偷渡者闖入美國境內。特朗普在佛州對記者說：「如果他們（美軍）需要使用『致命武器』，我已經批准他們使用。但我希望他們毋須這樣做。」特朗普又警告，如果非法移民衝擊美國邊界情況失控，美國將關閉整條美墨邊界。目前，美墨邊境派駐五千八百名美軍。在周四，數以百計的非法移民聚集墨西哥邊境小鎮蒂華納，準備過橋進入美國。美國邊防部隊和國民警衞軍嚴陣以待，氣氛緊張。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/特朗普准用致命武器對付人蛇-221224917.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E5%87%86%E7%94%A8%E8%87%B4%E5%91%BD%E6%AD%A6%E5%99%A8%E5%B0%8D%E4%BB%98%E4%BA%BA%E8%9B%87-221224917.html&d=OG2FKvExQ3NIMvp287CNawHZiNw4JStbf0cW9gpNrZc%3D&h=5ec7b1cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/特朗普准用致命武器對付人蛇-221224917.html</a>"},{"pid":"3d678ed5e5af4b81387c41b3744ddfe7b0ea424a","tid":931985,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T11:45:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30c311a3b7e05de1b801ef34f87c6cec93f5a6ee","tid":931985,"uid":121146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T11:46:55.000Z","msg":"德政"},{"pid":"2b26162aeb6e86458d7bea91850f7f6b17d086f9","tid":931985,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T15:11:06.000Z","msg":"兩星期前新聞又再post?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ad6c932a1318b4076fef737026e769803ab4cea","tid":931985,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b26162aeb6e86458d7bea91850f7f6b17d086f9","tid":931985,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T1